********************************************* Checkout create order customer credit card UK***************************************************

Checkout create order customer credit card
1. Go to development.ariat.com
2. Choose UK
3. Login valid credentials
3. Go to Women category
4. Go to Accessories/Gloves
5. Choose a product, select size
6. Press "add to basket" button
7. Press 2x Checkout  
8. Choose address
9. Press "next payment"
10. Enter payment methods details (card name, credit card no, type, expiration month, expiration year, security code
11. Press review order
12. Place order
